schemaVersion: 1
id: wedding-planner-root
name: Wedding Planner
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  A complete wedding-planning OS in a directory. Fill in three placeholders (who
  you are, your vision, your budget + date), run the bootstrap prompt, and a
  planner agent builds your vendor matrix, budget tracker, 18-month timeline,
  guest-list scaffold, vow + speech generators, RSVP system, and a day-of
  runbook. One agent, two routines, complete sanity in the chaos.
entry: index.md
